StudentMetrics

Academic Reporting meets Business Intelligence via Rails 3 and AJAX

StudentMetrics  supplies schools with a data repository to upload academic
data from various sources and apply BI and KPI's to the academic results.

The tools provide proactive dashboards for students, classes, year groups,
schools and teachers.

Reports are able to be printed and used as end of year.

Students are able to be transferred between schools prior to starting to
allow new schools to actively review the students prior to starting

Students can their full school scores with them for life. 